'''César Paes''' (yavutse 1959), ni umukinnyi wa filimi ukomoka muri [[Burezile|Burezire]] ariko utuye [[Bufaransa|mubufaransa]] .  Yayoboye inyandiko nyinshi zamamaye cyane zirimo: ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' , ''Mahaleo'' na ''L'opéra du bout du monde'' . Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni numuproducer, umwanditsi akaba na cinematografi. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
César Paes yavutse mu 1955 i Campos, [[Rio de Janeiro]], [[Burezili]]. 

Yashakanye na [[Marie-Clémence Paes|Marie-Clémence Andriamonta]], akaba n'umuyobozi wa Franco-Malagasy. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1988, yatangije isosiyete yigenga itanga umusaruro ikorera i Paris yitwa Laterit Productions hamwe n'umugore we Marie.  Isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa yiyemeje gukwirakwiza no gutangaza. Hamwe numugore we Marie, yayoboye documentaire nka ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Umugani wo muri [[Madagasikari]]'' , ''Ku barwanyi bacecetse'', ''Saudade do Futuro'' ''n'indirimbo za [[Madagasikari]]'' batsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Cinéma du Réel, Festival dei Popoli na Dok Leipzig .

Mu mwaka wa 2012, yafatanije kuyobora documentaire ''L'Opéra du bout du monde'' ikaba ari inkuru yo gushiraho opera yo muri iki gihe kuva ku kirwa cya Reunion ivuga ko abapolisi ba Louis XIV bageze mu birwa byo mu nyanja y'Abahinde. 

